[background arg="res://assets/art/backgrounds/Cafe_Background.png" fade="1.5" wait="true"]
if {Drink.Rating} == "none":
	jump begin_timeline
else:
	jump drink_rating
label begin_timeline
audio music "res://assets/audio/cafe_bgm.ogg" [fade="2.0" volume="-8.0"]
# DAY 4, SCENE 2
join GG (Happy) center
GG: Hello again! It's so good to see you again. I hope things are just fantastic?
Player: [pause=.3]Hello again GG. It's good to see you, too. Things are fine. Still a bit odd of a time but can't complain too much about the job.
Player: It's nice seeing the people as always. Like yourself.
GG: Oh my gosh, thank you so much for saying so. It feels so good to be included.
GG: I'm glad you enjoy seeing me cause I very much enjoy seeing you.
GG: I mean... how could I not enjoy a place like this and service like yours?
Player: I’m glad you feel that way. You should always feel at home here.
GG: Oh, I very much do.
GG (Sad): I just wish there was a good way to help you. Given how nice you have been to me and all.
Player: I appreciate that. But unless you can tell me who is behind turning Humans into Cats, I’m afraid there isn’t much that can be done.
GG (Neutral): Oh, I don't know about that.
GG: But If you want to serve me one of those fantastic drinks of yours, I might spill some beans on what I know about such people.
[signal arg="drink_hint"]
GG: Anything but matcha, it's too performative and fancy. Emphasis on avoiding silly fancy stuff.
leave GG
[signal arg="craft_drink"]
label drink_rating (Scene 2 Drink Rating)
[background arg="res://assets/art/backgrounds/Cafe_Background.png" fade="1.5" wait="true"]
audio music "res://assets/audio/craft_drink_bgm.ogg" [fade="2.0" volume="-5.0"]
if {Drink.Rating} == "mediocre":
	join GG center
	GG (Neutral): Pretty decent drink, thank you.
	GG: Another thing I've heard about people that turn humans into cats… they seem to like things on the more elegant side of the line.
	GG: Anyways, thanks for the drink.
	leave GG
	[signal arg="clear_drink"]
elif {Drink.Rating} == "good":
	join GG center
	GG (Happy): That’s a [speed=5]realllllly [speed=1]good drink, thank you.
	GG (Neutral): Another thing I've heard about people that turn humans into cats… that just like them, they like their drinks pretty fancy overall. Nothing crazy, but still. [speed=5]Fancy.
	GG (Neutral): Anyways, thanks for the drink.
	leave GG
	[signal arg="clear_drink"]
else:
	# Bad
	join GG (Sad) center
	GG: Oh, I really hate so much to be rude, but this isn't quite what I asked for. Could you perhaps try again? Thanks!
	leave GG
	[signal arg="clear_drink"]
	[signal arg="craft_drink"]
[signal arg="end_encounter"]
[end_timeline]